title: Sword of Sherwood Forest (1960 - UK) [Hammer Films]

Sword of Sherwood Forest (1960 - UK)

Adventure

starring . . . . Richard Greene, Peter Cushing, Niall MacGinnis
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054358/


A Hammer Film Production

Filmed at Powerscourt Estate, Enniskerry, County Wicklow, Ireland

When the sheriff of Nottingham schemes to assassinate an archbishop who opposes his greedy plan to seize the estate of a dead crusader, brave Robin Hood poses as the would-be killer to thwart the plot. But believing that Robin means to go through with the murder, Maid Marian takes matters into her own hands.
